Trinity::

She smiled. "He likes frogs? Well, they are a good animal to become." 
she giggled a little. She thought it was funny to want to be a frog, 
but she didn't want to insult the other bots. 
"Well, what do you like. You can be a wolf, or a badger, or a dear. 
How about a big animal? Like an elephant, or a lion. Yeah, lions are 
cool. Or how about a sabertooth tiger, like me." she smiled really 
big, showing her long fangs.
